{"tha-ap45:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap45:0.2":"Upalivagga ","tha-ap45:0.3":"3 Kaligodhaputtabhaddiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap45:1.1":"“Padumuttarasambuddham, ","tha-ap45:1.2":"mettacittam mahamunim; ","tha-ap45:1.3":"Upeti janata sabba, ","tha-ap45:1.4":"sabbalokagganayakam. ","tha-ap45:2.1":"Sattukanca baddhakanca, ","tha-ap45:2.2":"amisam panabhojanam; ","tha-ap45:2.3":"Dadanti satthuno sabbe, ","tha-ap45:2.4":"punnakkhette anuttare. ","tha-ap45:3.1":"Ahampi danam dassami, ","tha-ap45:3.2":"devadevassa tadino; ","tha-ap45:3.3":"Buddhasettham nimantetva, ","tha-ap45:3.4":"sanghampi ca anuttaram. ","tha-ap45:4.1":"Uyyojita maya cete, ","tha-ap45:4.2":"nimantesum tathagatam; ","tha-ap45:4.3":"Kevalam bhikkhusanghanca, ","tha-ap45:4.4":"punnakkhettam anuttaram. ","tha-ap45:5.1":"Satasahassapallankam, ","tha-ap45:5.2":"sovannam gonakatthatam; ","tha-ap45:5.3":"Tulikapatalikaya, ","tha-ap45:5.4":"khomakappasikehi ca; ","tha-ap45:5.5":"Maharaham pannapayim, ","tha-ap45:5.6":"asanam buddhayuttakam. ","tha-ap45:6.1":"Padumuttaro lokavidu, ","tha-ap45:6.2":"devadevo narasabho; ","tha-ap45:6.3":"Bhikkhusanghaparibyulho, ","tha-ap45:6.4":"mama dvaramupagami. ","tha-ap45:7.1":"Paccuggantvana sambuddham, ","tha-ap45:7.2":"lokanatham yasassinam; ","tha-ap45:7.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap45:7.4":"abhinamayim sangharam. ","tha-ap45:8.1":"Bhikkhunam satasahassam, ","tha-ap45:8.2":"buddhanca lokanayakam; ","tha-ap45:8.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap45:8.4":"paramannena tappayim. ","tha-ap45:9.1":"Padumuttaro lokavidu, ","tha-ap45:9.2":"ahutinam patiggaho; ","tha-ap45:9.3":"Bhikkhusanghe nisiditva, ","tha-ap45:9.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap45:10.1":"‘Yenidam asanam dinnam, ","tha-ap45:10.2":"sovannam gonakatthatam; ","tha-ap45:10.3":"Tamaham kittayissami, ","tha-ap45:10.4":"sunatha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap45:11.1":"Catusattatikkhattum so, ","tha-ap45:11.2":"devarajjam karissati; ","tha-ap45:11.3":"Anubhossati sampattim, ","tha-ap45:11.4":"accharahi purakkhato. ","tha-ap45:12.1":"Padesarajjam sahassam, ","tha-ap45:12.2":"vasudham avasissati; ","tha-ap45:12.3":"Ekapannasakkhattunca, ","tha-ap45:12.4":"cakkavatti bhavissati. ","tha-ap45:13.1":"Sabbasu bhavayonisu, ","tha-ap45:13.2":"uccakuli bhavissati; ","tha-ap45:13.3":"So ca paccha pabbajitva, ","tha-ap45:13.4":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap45:13.5":"Bhaddiyo nama namena, ","tha-ap45:13.6":"hessati satthu savako’. ","tha-ap45:14.1":"Vivekamanuyuttomhi, ","tha-ap45:14.2":"pantasenanivasaham; ","tha-ap45:14.3":"Phalancadhigatam sabbam, ","tha-ap45:14.4":"cattaklesomhi ajjaham. ","tha-ap45:15.1":"Mama sabbam abhinnaya, ","tha-ap45:15.2":"sabbannu lokanayako; ","tha-ap45:15.3":"Bhikkhusanghe nisiditva, ","tha-ap45:15.4":"etadagge thapesi mam. ","tha-ap45:16.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap45:16.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap45:16.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap45:17.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma bhaddiyo kaligodhaya putto thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap45:18.1":"Bhaddiyassa kaligodhaya puttattherassapadanam tatiyam. "}